Class ServiceController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsb.cs56.games.client_server.v2.server.Controllers.ServiceController
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChatController

    public abstract class ServiceController
extends java.lang.Object
    Service is an abstract class to be extended by all services a service is the server-side connection between a client and the server's copy of a game, passing data from the client to the game, as delegated by the clientconnect object on the server
    Version:
    for CS56, Spring 2013
    Author:
    Joseph Colicchio, Adam Ehrlich
